131
00:07:39.072 --> 00:07:42.412
And this is the work of a pharmacology team led by Jake.

132
00:07:42.992 --> 00:07:44.092
And what you can see is that

133
00:07:45.072 --> 00:07:48.352
in this one validation experiment, they were able to

134
00:07:49.072 --> 00:07:52.872
inducibly suppress the expression of Arnt using an inducible

135
00:07:52.952 --> 00:07:56.552
