141
00:08:15.312 --> 00:08:19.032
And so Arnt is an attractive target. That's how we felt about this.

142
00:08:19.412 --> 00:08:22.712
But there is a problem with this, and this is a problem that is shared with really

143
00:08:22.752 --> 00:08:24.312
