144
00:08:24.872 --> 00:08:27.012
Arnt is a classic undruggable protein.

145
00:08:27.592 --> 00:08:31.472
So it's a transcription factor, so it's buried inside the cell, can't be accessed

146
00:08:31.532 --> 00:08:35.352
with antibodies. You'll see that there's no

147
00:08:35.452 --> 00:08:38.232
catalytic activity. There are no obvious ligand binding pockets.

148
00:08:38.702 --> 00:08:42.452
And if you look at this structure of the protein Arnt bound to HIF-2

149
00:08:42.512 --> 00:08:46.162
alpha, what you'll see is that the biology of Arnt is

150
00:08:46.192 --> 00:08:49.332
mediated by protein-protein or protein-DNA interactions.

151
00:08:49.632 --> 00:08:53.312
So this is an extremely high bar, a classic undruggable.

152
00:08:53.352 --> 00:08:56.992
So it's a great candidate for a glue because of course the glues disregard all of

153
00:08:57.032 --> 00:08:58.772
the conventional rules of drug discovery.

154
00:08:59.572 --> 00:09:03.452
And the problem, of course, is that there was no precedent for a glue degrader for

155
00:09:03.492 --> 00:09:03.892
Arnt.

156
00:09:07.012 --> 00:09:10.952
More than 10 years ago, I came and visited the AACR to discuss this

157
00:09:11.032 --> 00:09:11.431
effort.

158
00:09:12.572 --> 00:09:14.132
There is a way of navigating

159
00:09:14.972 --> 00:09:18.692
prospectively target space through this degron approach, and we

