00:10:16.232 --> 00:10:16.732
project.

177
00:10:17.632 --> 00:10:21.592
And so at Neomorph, we wanted to have a really comprehensive survey

178
00:10:21.632 --> 00:10:24.052
for potential glue chemical matter for this target.

179
00:10:24.442 --> 00:10:26.432
And so what we did is we did a multi-pronged,

180
00:10:27.812 --> 00:10:30.012
very extensive screening effort.

181
00:10:30.092 --> 00:10:33.392
And so there is a cellular degradation screen is shown on the left.

