00:11:45.372 --> 00:11:49.092
and upon the cognate glue, you get robust ubiquitin transfer

204
00:11:49.172 --> 00:11:51.592
onto Arnt in this reconstituted

205
00:11:51.652 --> 00:11:55.184
system.This tells us that we have a good

