00:12:04.544 --> 00:12:07.424
the ARNT protein, but we weren't clear on how.

210
00:12:07.464 --> 00:12:11.424
And also this information is not a resolution that is sufficient to support

211
00:12:12.144 --> 00:12:13.824
a structure-based drug design campaign.

212
00:12:14.364 --> 00:12:17.464
And so our Cryo-EM team, led by Andres,

