00:13:33.684 --> 00:13:37.204
It's more than a log unit of separation from the next proteins that are degraded,

235
00:13:37.924 --> 00:13:41.484
and we don't consider there to be any liability associated with these proteins.

236
00:13:41.984 --> 00:13:45.584
When you go into in vitro assays and you look for the HIF-2A-dependent

