00:42:22.516 --> 00:42:26.216
a lesser extent of the CD4s that seems to be

719
00:42:26.256 --> 00:42:27.496
delivering sufficiently

720
00:42:28.536 --> 00:42:32.156
on what they do to preserve the durability.

721
00:42:32.756 --> 00:42:36.372
But it's a good question. Yeah.The center?

