00:42:36.582 --> 00:42:37.832
I can't see anything.

723
00:42:37.852 --> 00:42:41.822
Have you done any comparison to detuned CD3 affinity

724
00:42:41.892 --> 00:42:44.152
binders or any comparison of the Sineo Bio

