01:08:09.916 --> 01:08:13.465
Different though, is our ability to localize the degradation,

1157
01:08:13.976 --> 01:08:17.616
and we do this through the selection of our degrading receptor from our

1158
01:08:17.656 --> 01:08:18.456
EpiAtlas.

