1199
01:10:51.876 --> 01:10:55.856
on the cells, both at the single-cell level by RNA, but

1200
01:10:55.936 --> 01:10:57.176
also by IHC.

1201
01:10:59.396 --> 01:11:03.256
Through this evaluation, we identified a degrading receptor that had the

